<plot>'Hot Afternoons Have Been in Montana' is a dramatic and colorful montage combining photographs, computer art, and live-action to show how a hot afternoon in Montana is related to the whole world. It deeply honors the earth - its land, its history, its people, as it takes us on a wonderfully, meaningful odyssey through the world of time and space.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?246210</url></doc>
